**1v1 versus mode engaged! Play Project Freefall now with 2 players +!**


# Dive into Project Freefall! 🪂🪂

Free to play in Alpha, where the stakes are as high as the altitude. Plummet towards the earth in this adrenaline-pumping game of tag... but there’s only ONE parachute. You got this! 👍🏻

[media]


# Grenades, Sharks, and...A fire extinguisher? ⁉️⁉️☠️

 Toss a grenade, spray a fire extinguisher, or dodge the shark as you weave through the clouds in a high-speed aerial chase where alliances are temporary and gravity is permanent. 

[media]

# FEATURES

**More players mean more chaos!**

👯👯2-8-Player Mayhem: Invite your squad for the ultimate test of friendship and reflexes. 

🪂Cross-Platform Play: Dive in from either PC or VR. Everyone plays together in the same sky.

[media]

💬In-game Voice Chat: Talk with your friends!

😅High-Stakes, Simple Rules - don't splat!

👔Flex Your Style: Customize your look!

[media]

**What are you waiting for? Download for free and join our Discord.**

# It’s a race to the bottom - will you land with a prize or a splat?

[media]
